{"h16f41914g184dg46f8g9ba4g7d85432d570d": ["*The corpse seems willing to speak - but not to its killer.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_ZhentDungeon_DoubtingArtist_Dead.html", "e5ee4f3f-9fc3-4e71-8df0-6c3965eb18af"], "hbde75075g9798g4403g94c1g6f52c1db1ff1": ["*The corpse does not stir. It will answer no more questions.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_ZhentDungeon_DoubtingArtist_Dead.html", "b6154ada-efc4-4309-82ec-416a143b9707"], "hc6249ecfg86c8g4685gb7c3gaf24d436c66d": ["*The corpse regards you lifelessly.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_ZhentDungeon_DoubtingArtist_Dead.html", "b631c755-d94c-4a9b-85ba-c84647bd2ce3"], "h0b44c3eeg0d89g4d58gbaedg8d7f1bd1c225": ["Who are you?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_ZhentDungeon_DoubtingArtist_Dead.html", "b93d95a9-f16d-43b3-876b-b5d4bf73577d"], "h8806bbbbg8a97g4f8dga64cg81676d136f9e": ["Oskar Fevras... greatest artist... alive...", "3ae152be-8ff6-420c-81a0-68d6a55cd5bd", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_ZhentDungeon_DoubtingArtist_Dead.html", "ab5de7d7-ef4d-42c3-8ba8-17cf77fa0f57"], "hac8322c3g4336g47c0g9774g89f56ad2fcf3": ["You do know you're not alive anymore, right?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_ZhentDungeon_DoubtingArtist_Dead.html", "9f8d7700-83f9-495c-8f7a-44ce80426af8"], "h4adef17bgc279g4401ga81ag3944c2526ab6": ["... peculiar... sense of humour...", "3ae152be-8ff6-420c-81a0-68d6a55cd5bd", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_ZhentDungeon_DoubtingArtist_Dead.html", "bb33dd5a-c809-44f1-9478-68274ec9c47a"], "h8f033016g879dg45bfg831cga4595973e82a": ["Where did you keep your valuables?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_ZhentDungeon_DoubtingArtist_Dead.html", "7fd20158-1b09-446e-b5b2-c3ce4bf3c9f4"], "hc036044fg049bg4151ga969g28f9e291b178": ["... these hands... this mind.... treasure enough for a king... ", "3ae152be-8ff6-420c-81a0-68d6a55cd5bd", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\